org.xchain.framework.security

Interface Identity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultIdentity, IdentityImpl

    public interface Identity
extends java.io.Serializable
    An Identity represents an authenticated user. Identitys have a Set of Permissions that dictate what actions they are allowed to perform.
    Author:
    Jason Rose, Christian Trimble
